Class GNSearchResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gracenote.mmid.MobileSDK.GNSearchResponse
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GNAlbumIDSearchResponse

    public class GNSearchResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for the metadata returned by a match generated from a recognition or search operation.

        public java.lang.String getArtistBiographyUrl()

Note: Enriched content URLs are temporary; therefore, the application must be configured to handle expired URLs. Please contact your Gracenote Professional Services representative to discuss best practices for temporary caching and error handling.
        Returns:
        String value of Artist Biography URL
